---
title: Chorizo Patatas Bravas with Baby Plum Tomatoes, Rocket and Garlic Aioli
description: Eva's Chorizo Patatas Bravas has been specially selected as part of our Chef’s Pick recipe range. Smoky and full of the flavours of Spain, these crispy potatoes and chorizo sauce - in Eva’s words - is “tapas made easy”.  A super tasty addition to your midweek menu to tuck in to.
